Author: hondaceviche
Text: The only thing I have to add is it'll be more damaging to your career if you're suddenly unable to work and THEN have to take time to go IP.  The earlier you get some kind of treatment (maybe just IP on weekends or overnight, they offer that here) the more manageable it'll be alongside work.

Author: shamsgirl
Text: It’s not really the same but I’m in high school and I previously participated in a study abroad scholarship program with the US government and in the future I’d like to do another + the peace corps, and government programs are really strict about health clearance. Ironically while I was studying abroad I didn’t count calories, didn’t generally stress about my weight, came home 5 lbs lighter and then started bingeing and gained it all back lmao
